748
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:34,539
[SPEAKER_13] Dupe li postoji neke, ili ne postoji?

749
00:30:34,539 --> 00:30:35,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ništa ne radimo.

750
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:37,559
