753
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:45,740
[SPEAKER_13] Vozio sam se po Zagrebačkoj

754
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:47,859
[SPEAKER_13] i spustio sam neka glupa muzika,

755
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:50,420
[SPEAKER_13] spustim volan, ovo je volan, prozor

756
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:54,000
