759
00:30:59,839 --> 00:31:00,740
[SPEAKER_13] u auto koje mi je išao.

760
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:03,619
[SPEAKER_13] Nije za odraslog muškarca da plaće,

761
00:31:03,619 --> 00:31:04,420
