762
00:31:04,420 --> 00:31:05,759
[SPEAKER_13] Ovi su valjda mislili iz drugog auto

763
00:31:05,759 --> 00:31:06,500
[SPEAKER_13] da mi neko umro.

764
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:09,339
[SPEAKER_13] Ja sam tako 20 minuta do doma,

765
00:31:09,339 --> 00:31:10,339
