782
00:31:43,299 --> 00:31:46,279
[SPEAKER_13] moram bit radostan nak' mi je obitelj dobro.

783
00:31:46,279 --> 00:31:48,240
[SPEAKER_13] Biću radostan kad mi bude dobar posao.

784
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:50,000
