818
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:50,539
[SPEAKER_13] već sam otišao pred dalekom.

819
00:32:50,539 --> 00:32:52,140
[SPEAKER_13] Baš je o plakanju.

820
00:32:52,140 --> 00:32:54,579
[SPEAKER_13] Korago, ispašću odeku.

821
00:32:54,859 --> 00:32:55,640
[SPEAKER_03] Pozdrav svima.

822
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:56,579
