884
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:21,400
[SPEAKER_02] Ne o našim obrazcima.

885
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:24,380
[SPEAKER_02] Samo dajte mikrofon.

886
00:35:24,739 --> 00:35:26,840
