895
00:35:45,659 --> 00:35:47,639
[SPEAKER_03] I mislim da je ono,

896
00:35:47,639 --> 00:35:48,960
[SPEAKER_03] to sam htjela ono,

897
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:51,000
[SPEAKER_03] zašto muškarci ne bi plakali?

898
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:53,119
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, ispričavam se krivo svojom.

899
00:35:53,119 --> 00:35:55,420
