924
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:07,260
[SPEAKER_13] A zašto vjeruješ? Da budeš poseban.

925
00:37:07,260 --> 00:37:08,699
[SPEAKER_13] Da budeš važan.

926
00:37:08,699 --> 00:37:11,280
[SPEAKER_13] A zašto želimo biti posebni i važni?

927
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:13,599
